snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: Zodiac: Orcanon Odyssey | PS4, PS VITA Trailer
snippet.description:
Be ready to explore the world or Orcanon on PS4 and PS VITA! 
http://zodiac.kobojo.com/

Set off on an epic journey to discover the hidden truths of Orcanon and the secrets of your own past. Experience a captivating story, discover vast new lands and fantastic creatures, meet terrifying foes and unforgettable allies.

The adventure begins on PS4 and PS VITA in 2016!

http://zodiac.kobojo.com/
